    <item>
      <title>股市、债券齐跌，创数十年来最差开局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/stocks-bonds-drop-in-tandem-for-worst-start-to-year-in-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们希望年底泛市场反弹能够在2024年的第一个交易日继续上涨，但他们却得到了相反的结果，这一交易日股市和债券出现了开年以来最严重的一致下跌之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/stocks-bonds-drop-in-tandem-for-worst-start-to-year-in-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:40:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗的红海权力游戏引发了对贸易中断的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/iran-s-red-sea-power-play-heightens-fears-of-trade-disruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向红海派遣一艘军舰是迄今为止在关键贸易路线上挑战美军的最大胆举动，这让胡塞武装分子更加胆大妄为，他们的导弹在过去两个月扰乱了航运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/iran-s-red-sea-power-play-heightens-fears-of-trade-disruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:20:06 GMT</pubDate>
